WARNING: This project is no longer supported, because Drupal 6 is too old.

Usage: drush make https://raw.github.com/kratocz/drush-make-pressflow-6/master/make.ini [DIR]

* [DIR]: Specified directory instead of current directory where the platform will be placed (optional).

...will download complete Pressflow 6 platform to the new directory DIR (or to current directory).

Use this only at your own risk!
